Name:           Fire Element
Short Name:     fire
Level Required: 15

Description:
  Raw elemental Fire in living form, the Fire Element can blast its
  enemies with fireballs and engulf them in choking smoke and flame.

Commands:
  - summon fire:    Summons it to you         (costs 100 sp)
  - catt <monster>: Makes it attack <monster> (costs 10 sp)
  - cstop:          Makes it stop fighting    (costs 20 sp)
  - ban fire:       Banishes it               (costs 30 sp)
